excerpt.rendered:
2019 Tesla Model X Performance Pearl White Multi Coat on All Black

Price : Rp 4 M On The Road Jakarta

KM 17.500 an (on going)
Performance Type (Dual Motor All Wheel Drive)
Exterior Color : Pearl White Multi Coat
Interior Color : All Black
22″ Onyx Black Wheels
Six Seat Interior

*Open Pre-Order for The 2022 Tesla Model X!* Get yours now!

Tesla Model X Price
– Long Range : Rp 3 M (basic price before option)
– Plaid : Rp 4.4 M (basic price before option)

Terdapat dua pilihan tipe Tesla Model X yaitu tipe Long Range Plus (Dual Motor All Wheel Drive) & tipe Performance (Dual Motor All Wheel Drive)

Tersedia dalam pilihan warna eksterior : Red Multi Coat, Pearl White Multi Coat, Deep Blue Metallic, Midnight Silver Metallic, & Solid Black

Jarak tempuh : 597 KM (Long Range Plus) & 483 KM (Performance)

0 – 100 km/jam : 4.4 detik (Long Range Plus) & 2.6 detik (Performance with Ludicrous Mode)

Kecepatan puncak : 249 km/jam (Long Range Plus) & 262 km/jam (Performance)

Pilihan velg yang tersedia : 20″ Silver Wheels & 22″ Onyx Black Wheels

Pilihan warna interior :
All Black – Figured Ash Wood Decor
Black and White – Dark Ash Wood Decor
Cream – Oak Wood Decor
All Black – Carbon Fiber Decor (Available for Performance Type Only)
Black and White – Carbon Fiber Decor (Available for Performance Type Only)

Pilihan jumlah seats : Five Seats, Six Seats, & Seven Seats

Mobil Bebas Ganjil Genap
Jarak tempuh 505 KM
Waktu pengecasan 5-6 jam
Biaya pengecasan ketika dikonversi ke dalam rupiah Rp 140.000
0 – 100 km/jam : 2.7 detik
Kecepatan tertinggi : 250 km/jam
Integrated monitor in 17 inch touchscreen
Include Autopilot Mode
Smart Air Suspension System
Free Wall Charger & Installation
2 Tahun Warranty Full Cover kecuali yang habis pakai
8 Tahun Warranty khusus buat baterai mobil
